{"tid":1377575,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有五毛係高登爆大鑊︰老實講，被帶風向帶得最多的，是警隊","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:29:31.000Z","uid":25797,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"43fee11ffa701bd680527b27df1b40db253be349","tid":1377575,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"由於論壇：高登、連登。好多人都漸漸識穿五毛帶風向的手法。加上在高登被強力封鎖，所以好多五毛都轉戰Facebook,IG,TG<br />\n<br />\n而高層呢兩個月比打手的重點任務是：針隊所有警隊Page，警隊內部群組。<br />\n<br />\n一。煽動警察對示威者的仇恨<br />\n二。發出大量要暴打示威者等言論<br />\n三。令警隊認為自己是維持治安的英雄，示威者是邪惡一方<br />\n四。在警隊內部發佈「打得愈勁、捉得愈多、升得愈高」等消息<br />\n五。即使使用過份武力，中央依然會支持警隊<br />\n<br />\n總之成個手法正如當年宣導紅衛兵去鬥地主一樣。現在我們五毛的高層對於警隊的思想改造非常滿意，進入收成期，即使沒有五毛干預，警隊已經自發仇恨示威者。這是低學歷低智商的警隊，無法察覺的情緒黑洞，成功被卷進黨的思想鬥爭法之中。"},{"pid":"258b8887227f9439154ac03fd759b71affd22b69","tid":1377575,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:08:48.000Z","msg":"source : <a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7091310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D7091310&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDW8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=5f5b6051\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7091310</a>"},{"pid":"d2c2ca8888a3473571ad5a3d0aca83cd81e9014a","tid":1377575,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c189b1441f256c5c7e9a6d755d33b5eb143e9100","tid":1377575,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f56c35fdc4d510fd221690c4e5cabb7b1c4a64","tid":1377575,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0869d96